title: Openstreetmap, Hungary Natural Areas,Hungary, 2008
name: Openstreetmap, Hungary Natural Areas,Hungary, 2008
description: This data was provided by Openstreetmaps and contains detailed information on the Natural Areas in the country of Hungary. Natural areas include parks, forests, riverbanks, and water.
